description:
Mr. D is a Canadian sitcom television series starring comedian Gerry Dee. The series follows the misadventures of a strange schoolteacher named Gerry Duncan, nicknamed Mr. D. It debuted on CBC on January 9, 2012


S02E01 Gerry's Evaluation:

When Gerry is evaluated by a member of the board, he must go out of his way to prove that he is great at his job, or risk severe punishment.
